When attempting to generate a specification from annotated code where a runtime.File is involved, go-swagger exits with "can't determine selector path from runtime".

## Steps to reproduce
Create one file, with the following contents

package bug                                                                 
                                                                                
import "github.com/go-openapi/runtime"                                          
                                                                                
// swagger:parameters test                                                      
type TestRequest struct {                                                       
    // A file                                                                   
    //                                                                          
    // in:formData                                                              
    // required: true                                                           
    File runtime.File `json:"file"`                                             
}

Run `swagger generate spec`.

